description: A local birdwatcher says he would never have seen the bird of prey had he not been amid lockdown.
title: Rare black-winged kite spotted in Alderney
title_page: Rare black-winged kite spotted in Alderney - BBC News
maintext: He said he happened to look up to see the bird "coming in over the sea", adding: "If I wasn't on lockdown I wouldn't have seen it."
